description:
Bratz: Flaunt Your Fashion - Pretty 'N' Punk Fashion Pack! Unleash your inner rebel with punkalicious outfits from the iconic Pretty ‘N’ Punk collection. 

Strut your stuff on the catwalk in the new minigame, showcasing your style and attitude. Party like a punk and show everyone who rules the runway! 

PARTY PUNK OUTFITS – Unlock outfits from the Pretty ‘N’ Punk Collection, featuring Sasha’s new look! 

ROCK THE RUNWAY – Strike a pose and impress the judges in the catwalk minigame 

CREATE UNIQUE LOOKS – Show your stylin’ self-expression with new makeup looks and punkalicious hairstyles
name: Bratz®: Flaunt your fashion - Pretty 'N' Punk Fashion Pack
